  "texts": [
    "In this way, interpretability looks for well informed understanding instead of just anticipations.",
    "REAL-TIME DECISION-MAKINGDynamic educational environments require reinforcement learning systems capable of making real-time decisions.",
    "Existing algorithms often struggle with high computational demands and slow adaptation to new data.",
    "Online learning methods offer a solution by enabling models to update incrementally as new information becomes available, reducing the need for complete retraining.",
    "Realtime decision-making is particularly valuable for adaptive learning platforms and crisis management, where immediate responsiveness is critical."
  ]
}